        "heading": "RIDE RFN - Powerful Electric Dirt Bikes made for the Western United States",
        "heading_color": "#ffffff",
        "body": "<h4>In the past few years, we’ve witnessed an explosion of electric motos. They’re everywhere - on streets, trails, and tracks. Yet most e-motos are nothing more than a mountain bike with a motor on it. Fun, yes - but far from functional when it comes to serious trail riding or motocross racing.<br/><br/>That’s where our vision began. The goal behind the RFN Warrior Series was bold: to create the ultimate line of purpose-built electric dirt bikes - machines engineered for real riders of every size, age, and skill level. Not toys, not compromises - true electric motocross bikes that are head-to-head with gas competition.<br/><br/>After two years and millions of dollars invested in research and development, that vision has become reality. The RFN Warrior Series is here - four models that set a new benchmark for electric dirt bikes, combining championship-level performance, advanced battery technology, and precision engineering into one unstoppable lineup available for order online or in authorized dealerships across Utah and Idaho.</h4>",
        "alignment": "center",
        "max_width": 720
      }
